{
  "stem": "5911.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wouldn't-- my mother wouldn't hear of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We wanted to leave, leave Europe, leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wandering through Poland during this 10, 11-month period, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were other people milling around, chaos.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chaos.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Chaos, chaos, chaos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going to sleep.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know when-- where we were going to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But people stuck together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You met people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This one gave you an idea, this one gave you an idea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we also wanted to go out of the Russian sector, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was-- pushed us on to go to-- and then we found that there was the displaced persons camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "DP camps in Bad Gastein, Austria, was a very nice place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very anti-Semitic, especially the Lith-- especially the Lithuanians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They killed quite a few people after the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm sorry that I have to mention, but it is the truth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Lithuanians were very big anti-- anti-Semites, and--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Polish also.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Ukrainian also.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Lithuanians, in my experience, were the most.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The administration, Jewish administration in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget, there had to be-- somebody took charge.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Somebody had to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to save [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], the rest of the-- the remnants of-- of-- of the-- of the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to save, so there were-- there were like-- people were helping-- helping each other a great deal to-- to-- to-- to come to something.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when-- and we went to Bad Gastein, which again, my mother became a nurse again in the infirmary, and I met a lady.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In fact, I met a lady at the 50th anniversary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were with her in Bad Gastein, but she tells the story at a 50th.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Her name is Eisner.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
